<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT10">
<l>āṅkāra vāra matukēṭ ṭaḻalumiḻum</l>
<l>pūṅkā raravaṇaiyāṉ poṉmēṉi yāṅkāṇa</l>
<l>vallamē yallamē māmalarāṉ vārcaṭaiyāṉ</l>
<l>vallarē yallarē vāḻttu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Are we not capable of seeing the golden body of Him on the bed</l>
<l>that is the beautiful [but] hostile erpent which spits fire,</l>
<l rend="indent">hearing the loud noise then?</l>
<l>[Brahmā] on the big flower [and Śiva] with long matted locks</l>
<l>are not capable of praising [Him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
